;(n,)&nbsp;where&nbsp;n&nbsp;</span><span class="mtk21">is&nbsp;the&nbsp;number&nbsp;of&nbsp;samples</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk21">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;testdata:&nbsp;numpy&nbsp;array&nbsp;of&nbsp;shape&nbsp;(m,d)&nbsp;where&nbsp;m&nbsp;i</span><span class="mtk21">s&nbsp;the&nbsp;number&nbsp;of&nbsp;test&nbsp;samples&nbsp;and&nbsp;d&nbsp;is&nbsp;the&nbsp;number&nbsp;o</span><span class="mtk21">f&nbsp;features</span></span><br><span><span></span></span><br><span><span class="mtk21">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;returns:&nbsp;the&nbsp;predicted&nbsp;labels&nbsp;for&nbsp;the&nbsp;test&nbsp;dat</span><span class="mtk21">a&nbsp;which&nbsp;is&nbsp;a&nbsp;random&nbsp;label&nbsp;from&nbsp;the&nbsp;training&nbsp;data</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk21">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;"""</span></span><br><span><span></span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;classes&nbsp;=&nbsp;np.unique(trainlabel)</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;rints&nbsp;=&nbsp;rng.integers(low=</span><span class="mtk12">0</span><span class="mtk1">,&nbsp;high=</span><span class="mtk15">len</span><span class="mtk1">(classes),&nbsp;size=</span><span class="mtk15">len</span><span class="mtk1">(testdata))</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;predlabel&nbsp;=&nbsp;classes[rints]</span></span><br><span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><span class="mtk19">return</span><span class="mtk1">&nbsp;predlabel</span></span><br></pre><colab-read-only-cell-placeholder style="display: none;"><template shadowrootmode="open"><!----><div><!--?lit$633059656$-->Start coding or <span role="button" class="link" tabindex="0">generate</span> with AI.</div></template></colab-read-only-cell-placeholder></pre></div><colab-form class="formview vertical layout flex"><div class="widget-area"></div></colab-form></div>
