  </button></template><md-icon aria-hidden="true"><template shadowrootmode="open"><!----><slot></slot></template>keyboard_arrow_down</md-icon></md-icon-button><h3>Questions</h3></div>
<ol>
<li>Does averaging the validation accuracy across multiple splits give more consistent results?</li>
<li>Does it give more accurate estimate of test accuracy?</li>
<li>What is the effect of the number of iterations on the estimate? Do we get a better estimate with higher iterations?</li>
<li>Consider the results you got for the previous questions. Can we deal with a very small train dataset or validation dataset by increasing the iterations?</li>
</ol>
